QuestData.Title: A Good Start
QuestData.Description: Regardless of our predicament, our orders stand. We are to learn the lay of this land and prepare it for Hellscream's fleet.$b$bBut first, we must deal with these savages!$b$bYou see these corpses I've stacked up around the camp? I want mountains of them!$b$bWe are the Horde!$b$bThese vermin have not learned to fear us yet, but we will fix that soon enough...
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 4 Hozen Mudflingers, 4 Hozen Skullthumpers, and 3 Hozen Fishcatchers.
